OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods for some with sunny spells for
OL,7,Fothers to end the day but remaining
OL,8,Fdry for all. Overnight clear spells
OL,9,Fdevelop with the wind easing in most
OL,10,Fplaces. A mild night in urban areas
OL,11,Fbut cooler in the country.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FDry with some hazy sunshine
OL,14,Fthroughout the day. Above average
OL,15,Ftemperatures, and becoming very warm
OL,16,For hot in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
